sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor USER as 👤 Cashier / Staff
    participant BR as Browser
    participant SPA as CRM Frontend SPA
    participant SSO as SSO Reborn<br/>(OAuth/OIDC)
    participant AUTH as Auth Service
    participant CFG as Config / Tenant API

    USER->>BR: Truy cập crm.reborn.vn
    BR->>SPA: GET / (index.html)
    SPA->>SPA: Check cookie token
    alt Chưa có token
      SPA->>SSO: Redirect /oauth/authorize<br/>client_id, redirect_uri
      SSO->>USER: Hiển thị form đăng nhập
      USER->>SSO: Nhập email + password
      SSO->>SSO: Xác thực + 2FA (nếu có)
      SSO-->>BR: Redirect callback?code=xxx
      BR->>SPA: /callback?code=xxx
      SPA->>AUTH: POST /authenticator/token<br/>{ code }
      AUTH->>SSO: Exchange code → access_token
      SSO-->>AUTH: access_token + refresh_token
      AUTH-->>SPA: Set cookie token + user info
    end
    SPA->>CFG: GET /api/user/profile
    CFG-->>SPA: { user, roles, tenants }
    SPA->>CFG: GET /api/tenant/config
    CFG-->>SPA: { features, permissions }
    SPA->>SPA: Init AuthContext + TenantContext
    SPA->>BR: Redirect /create_sale_add<br/>(POS default cho retail)
    BR->>USER: Hiển thị màn hình POS
